    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly, and the interior is clean with only minor signs of use. While there are a few small stone chips on the hood and light wear on the driver's seat bolster, the car is mechanically sound and ready for its next owner. It provides a comfortable, reliable driving experience and includes a complete service history.",
