    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is ideal for a dedicated hobbyist looking for a project or someone in need of a parts donor. It currently suffers from major mechanical setbacks, including an engine that requires a complete overhaul and a failing transmission. The exterior shows significant wear with heavy rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior has sustained considerable damage over the years. Please note that it is not currently in drivable condition and will need to be towed.",
